text: == Births == * March 8 – John III, Duke of Brittany (died 1341) * June 30 – John de Warenne, 8th Earl of Surrey, English politician (died 1347) * James Douglas the Black, Scottish patriot (died 1330) * Hugh the younger Despenser (died 1326) * Frederick I of Austria (died 1330) * William III, Count of Holland (died 1337)
